 Author: Tijo Joseph
 Date  : 19/11/2014
 Description : 
 call UpdatePassword()
 
 ChangeType -- 1 Normal Change Password
			-- 2 Updating OTP
			-- 3 Updating Pwaasword after generating OTP
 
